    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential emptiness and a sense of being a \"hollow shell,\" questioning the purpose of maintaining their physical body. The assistant responds with empathy, validating the user's pain while contextualizing it as a symptom of profound grief or mental distress rather than an absolute reality.",
